_sText:
"Brought to you by novalin, maker or de_residentevil.
novalin has been working on this original map for months (it actually started as a Hostage rescue map). It has been thoroughly play tested through 9 beta versions and is a favorite on our server. This map is best suited for 16-20 players. Game play is excellent. We have found this to be one of the most even maps available. It usually starts with either side winning 4-5 straight rounds, and then the other team makes a comeback. Tonight I added up the stats on our server and 720 rounds were played, and 360 were won by the T’s and 360 were won by CT’s. Please give it a try, you won’t be sorry." [Kas]

Created by dF|novalin / Brian Riggsbee
